*** Context ***
+ Clear Workspace
+ No Execution Environment is linked to the LDT

*** Actions ***
- Right-click in the Script Explorer
- New -> Lua Project
- Fill the name and click on "Configure Execution Environments..." -> "Add..."
- Select an Execution Environment to add -> Ok -> Ok -> Finish

*** Assertions ***
# The Execution Environment is linked to the LDT
# The Execution Environment is linked to the created Project
